      <section id="course-description">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Read a free sample from the book: <a style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700;" href="http://ui.thoughtbot.com/assets/backbone-js-on-rails-thoughtbot-ebook-august-2011-sample.html">HTML</a> | <a style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700;" href="http://ui.thoughtbot.com/assets/backbone-js-on-rails-thoughtbot-ebook-august-2011-sample.pdf">PDF</a></h3>
        <p>
          You build web apps, and you've seen the shift towards highly interactive, rich client-side web applications.  Over the past years, we've seen the same things, and have built our apps, processes, and best practices around this.  Learn the better way to build rich, interactive applications using Backbone.js and Rails.
