        <p>
          In addition to the book, you also get a complete example application, and the ability to get your questions about Backbone.js and Rails answered by the thoughtbot team. The book is written using <a href="https://github.com/schacon/git-scribe">git-scribe</a> on GitHub. When you purchase, we give you access directly to the repository, so you can use the GitHub comment and issue features to give us feedback about what we've written and what you'd like to see. Give us your toughest Backbone.js questions with GitHub issues, and we'll answer. Last but not least, also included is a complete sample Backbone.js and Rails application. What the book describes and explains, the example app demonstrates with real, working code. Fully up to date for Rails 3.1 and Backbone 0.9.1.
        </p>
