      <section id="benefits">
        <h3>You'll learn to&hellip;</h3>
        <dl>
          <dt><p>Deliver functionality on the client side for lightning fast applications and awesome native-app-like usability.</p></dt>
          <dd><p>Your customers use your app day-in and day-out: are they switching to the competition because your app is clunky, with full page refreshess and poor interactivity?  Push business logic into the browser and make your app crazy snappy.</p></dd>
          <dt><p>Build faster, more interactive web apps &mdash; even on mobile!</p></dt>
          <dd><p>Create mobile apps that load blazing fast: Backbone.js and its dependencies are super tiny.  Learn how to choose the right dependencies and shed even more KBs.</p></dd>
          <dt><p>Do it all without compromising and writing messy, disorganized code.</p></dt>
          <dd><p>Is your JavaScript-heavy web app getting out of control?  Technical debt everywhere?  Are you using the DOM for persistence, and going crazy with layers and layers of jQuery form-parsing and ajax-submitting code?  Clean up your client-side code by following conventions, using software patterns you're familiar with, and refactoring to reusable modules.</p></dd>
        </dl>
      </section>

